# 5. You'll find: <input name="security-token" type="hidden" value="..."/>
# 6. Copy the value and replace DDB_SECURITY_TOKEN above
# 7. Repeat for: authenticity-token and request-verification-token
#
# OR use the automation script:
#   poetry run python DNDBeyond/scripts/get_ddb_tokens.py
